{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe1e-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1015"},"text":"§ 1015.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Basis of property acquired by gifts and transfers in trust","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe1f-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Gifts after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1920-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1920","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"If the property was acquired by gift after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1920-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1920","children":[],"tail":", the basis shall be the same as it would be in the hands of the donor or the last preceding owner by whom it was not acquired by gift, except that if such basis (adjusted for the period before the date of the gift as provided in section 1016) is greater than the fair market value of the property at the time of the gift, then for the purpose of determining loss the basis shall be such fair market value. If the facts necessary to determine the basis in the hands of the donor or the last preceding owner are unknown to the donee, the Secretary shall, if possible, obtain such facts from such donor or last preceding owner, or any other person cognizant thereof. If the Secretary finds it impossible to obtain such facts, the basis in the hands of such donor or last preceding owner shall be the fair market value of such property as found by the Secretary as of the date or approximate date at which, according to the best information that the Secretary is able to obtain, such property was acquired by such donor or last preceding owner."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe20-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Transfer in trust after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1920-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1920","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"If the property was acquired after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1920-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1920","children":[],"tail":", by a transfer in trust (other than by a transfer in trust by a gift, bequest, or devise), the basis shall be the same as it would be in the hands of the grantor increased in the amount of gain or decreased in the amount of loss recognized to the grantor on such transfer under the law applicable to the year in which the transfer was made."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe21-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Gift or transfer in trust before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1921-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1921","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"If the property was acquired by gift or transfer in trust on or before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1920-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1920","children":[],"tail":", the basis shall be the fair market value of such property at the time of such acquisition."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe22-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Increased basis for gift tax paid","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe23-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"If—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe24-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the property is acquired by gift on or after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-09-02"},"text":"September 2, 1958","children":[],"tail":", the basis shall be the basis determined under subsection (a), increased (but not above the fair market value of the property at the time of the gift) by the amount of gift tax paid with respect to such gift, or"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe25-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the property was acquired by gift before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-09-02"},"text":"September 2, 1958","children":[],"tail":", and has not been sold, exchanged, or otherwise disposed of before such date, the basis of the property shall be increased on such date by the amount of gift tax paid with respect to such gift, but such increase shall not exceed an amount equal to the amount by which the fair market value of the property at the time of the gift exceeded the basis of the property in the hands of the donor at the time of the gift."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe26-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Amount of tax paid with respect to gift","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of paragraph (1), the amount of gift tax paid with respect to any gift is an amount which bears the same ratio to the amount of gift tax paid under chapter 12 with respect to all gifts made by the donor for the calendar year (or preceding calendar period) in which such gift is made as the amount of such gift bears to the taxable gifts (as defined in section 2503(a) but computed without the deduction allowed by section 2521) made by the donor during such calendar year or period. For purposes of the preceding sentence, the amount of any gift shall be the amount included with respect to such gift in determining (for the purposes of section 2503(a)) the total amount of gifts made during the calendar year or period, reduced by the amount of any deduction allowed with respect to such gift under section 2522 (relating to charitable deduction) or under section 2523 (relating to marital deduction).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe27-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Gifts treated as made one-half by each spouse","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of paragraph (1), where the donor and his spouse elected, under section 2513 to have the gift considered as made one-half by each, the amount of gift tax paid with respect to such gift under chapter 12 shall be the sum of the amounts of tax paid with respect to each half of such gift (computed in the manner provided in paragraph (2)).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe28-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Treatment as adjustment to basis","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of section 1016(b), an increase in basis under paragraph (1) shall be treated as an adjustment under section 1016(a).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe29-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Application to gifts before 1955","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"With respect to any property acquired by gift before 1955, references in this subsection to any provision of this title shall be deemed to refer to the corresponding provision of the Internal Revenue Code of 1939 or prior revenue laws which was effective for the year in which such gift was made.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe2a-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Special rule for gifts made after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1976","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe2b-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/6/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of any gift made after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1976","children":[],"tail":", the increase in basis provided by this subsection with respect to any gift for the gift tax paid under chapter 12 shall be an amount (not in excess of the amount of tax so paid) which bears the same ratio to the amount of tax so paid as—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe2c-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/6/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the net appreciation in value of the gift, bears to","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe2d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/6/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount of the gift.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe2e-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/d/6/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Net appreciation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of paragraph (1), the net appreciation in value of any gift is the amount by which the fair market value of the gift exceeds the donor’s adjusted basis immediately before the gift.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe2f-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1015/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Gifts between spouses","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of any property acquired by gift in a transfer described in section 1041(a), the basis of such property in the hands of the transferee shall be determined under section 1041(b)(2) and not this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id449ffe30-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736"},"text":"Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/68A/298"},"text":"68A Stat. 298","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/866/tI/s43/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–866, title I, § 43(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-09-02"},"text":"Sept. 2, 1958","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/72/1640"},"text":"72 Stat. 1640","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/614/tI/s102/d/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–614, title I, § 102(d)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-12-31"},"text":"Dec. 31, 1970","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/1841"},"text":"84 Stat. 1841","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/tXIX"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, title XIX","children":[],"tail":", §§ 1901(a)(122), 1906(b) (13)(A), title XX, § 2005(c), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-04"},"text":"Oct. 4, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/1784"},"text":"90 Stat. 1784","children":[],"tail":", 1834, 1877; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/34/tIV/s442/d/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–34, title IV, § 442(d)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/322"},"text":"95 Stat. 322","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/369/dA/tIV/s421/b/5"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–369, div. A, title IV, § 421(b)(5)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-07-18"},"text":"July 18, 1984","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/98/794"},"text":"98 Stat. 794","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id449ffe31-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id449ffe32-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id449ffe33-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 2521, referred to in subsec. (d)(2), was repealed by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/tXX/s2001/b/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, title XX, § 2001(b)(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-04"},"text":"Oct. 4, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/1849"},"text":"90 Stat. 1849","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Internal Revenue Code of 1939, referred to in subsec. (d)(5), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1939-02-10/ch2"},"text":"act Feb. 10, 1939, ch. 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/53/1"},"text":"53 Stat. 1","children":[],"tail":". Prior to the enactment of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 [formerly I.R.C. 1954], the 1939 Code was classified to former Title 26, Internal Revenue Code. For table of comparisons of the 1939 Code to the 1986 Code, see Table I preceding "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s1"},"text":"section 1 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id449ffe34-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id449ffe35-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1984—Subsec. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/369"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–369","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (e)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1981—Subsec. (d)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/34"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–34","children":[],"tail":" substituted “calendar year (or preceding calendar period)” for “calendar quarter (or calendar year if the gift was made before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1971-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1971","children":[],"tail":")” and “calendar year or period” for “calendar quarter or year” in two places."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1976—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/s1906/b/13/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, § 1906(b)(13)(A)","children":[],"tail":", struck out “or his delegate” after “Secretary” in four places."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d)(1)(A), (B). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/s1901/a/122"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, § 1901(a)(122)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “"},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-09-02"},"text":"September 2, 1958","children":[],"tail":"” for “the date of enactment of the Technical Amendments Act of 1958”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d)(6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/s2005/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, § 2005(c)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (6)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1970—Subsec. (d)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/614"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–614","children":[],"tail":" substituted “calendar quarter (or calendar year if the gift was made before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1971-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1971","children":[],"tail":")” for “calendar year” the first place it appears and “calendar quarter or year” for “calendar year” every other place it appears."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1958—Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/866"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–866","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (d)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id449ffe36-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id449ffe37-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1984 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/369"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–369","children":[],"tail":" applicable to transfers after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-07-18"},"text":"J